content:
[[module CSS]]

div.terminal{
    border: 1px solid black;
    border: solid 3px #000000;
    border-radius: 16px;
/* black shadow at the top of the terminal */
    background-color: #000000;
    background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 100% at 50% 90%, transparent, #000000);
    background-position: center;
    display: block;
/* shadow around the terminal */
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 10em 1em rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
/* prevents scanline from forming a scrollwheel */
    overflow:hidden;
}

div.scanline{

    margin-top: -40%;

    width: 100%;

    height: 60px;

    position: relative;

    pointer-events: none;

/* Safari 4.0 - 8.0 */

    -webkit-animation: scan 12s linear 0s infinite; /* You may need to change this. If the bar goes by too quickly, increase 5s. */

    animation: scan 12s linear 0s infinite; /* Same as above */

    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(243, 243, 202,0), rgba(243, 243, 202,0.1)) !important;

}
/* Safari 4.0 - 8.0 */

@-webkit-keyframes scan{

    from{ transform: translateY(-10%);}

    to{  transform: translateY(5000%);} /* You may need to change this depending on the length of your terminal. If the scanline stops halfway, increase the second number.*/

}



@keyframes scan{

    from{ transform: translateY(-10%);}

    to{  transform: translateY(5000%);} /* Same as above.*/

}

div.text{
    color: rgba(21, 153, 39);
    padding-top: 40%;
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1.2em;
    }

div.text a {
    color: #159927;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: transparent;
}
div.text a.newpage {
    color: #159927;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: transparent;
}
div.text a:hover {
    color: #159927;
    text-decoration: underline;
    background-color: #D9C56f;
    padding: 1px;
}
div.text a:hover::before{
content: "> ";
}
[[/module]]
[[div class="terminal"]]
[[div class="scanline"]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="text"]]
[[=]]
[[size 150%]] __FOUNDATION TERMINAL 0041__[[/size]]
@@ @@
[[div class="normalFontTime"]]
@@------@@
SECURE, CONTAIN, PROTECT
@@------@@
[[/div]]
[[/=]]
[[html]]
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.rawgit.com/deadsurgeon42/scp-sources/6cf60652/scp-4000-samualism/termynal.css" />
</head>
<body>

<style>
a {
    color: #159927;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: transparent;
}
a.newpage {
    color: #D9C56f;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: transparent;
}
a:hover {
    color: #977d45;
    text-decoration: underline;
    background-color: #D9C56f;
    padding: 1px;
}
a:hover::before{
content: "> ";
}
:root {
    --color-text: rgba(21, 153, 34);
    --color-text-subtle: rgba(21, 153, 34);
}

[data-termynal] {
    padding: 16px;
    border-radius: 0;

    background-color: transparent;
    color: rgba(21, 153, 34);

    width: 100%;
    font-size: 12px;
}

[data-termynal]:before {
    display: none;
}

</style>

<div id="termynal" data-termynal data-ty-typeDelay="110">
  <span data-ty="input" data-ty-prompt="Foundation Terminal 0041:">Online</span>
 <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Please look inside hole on top of terminal<br><br></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Ocular activity detected</span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Loading...</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Access Granted. Welcome, Doctor.</span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="" style="text-align: center;">Please choose a file</span>
  <span data-ty="input" data-ty-prompt=">">Outpost41</span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">The file requires: LEVEL 5 CLEARANCE. Please input your clearance. </span>
  <span data-ty="input" data-ty-prompt=">">abloodymoonandabeatensun</span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="" style="text-align: center;">Opening File...</span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Instructions:</span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">When The Child enters within 500 m of your base, activate the 250 lumen lights around base. This can be accomplished via control panel behind you.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Only attempt to repair lights during night. Spotlight Repair and Maintenance manual x0.87 can be found within top left drawer of desk. Tools can be found in toolbox besides terminal.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Eat only three cans of fruit/vegetables every day, which will last you for approximately 5 years. Use the farming chamber with the seeds found in the same area as the canned foods to grow more food. Get to a point where you can only eat two cans of fruit/vegetables and one serving of grown food every other day.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Pest control is not necessary.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">If The Child discovers your location and is not warded off by the lights, a pill can be found in the safe with combination code HFSE631 which causes a quick, painless death. Only use if The Child's presence is guaranteed and not an illusion.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="" style="text-align: center;">One (1) Additional Result: Note from "John Doe"</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
 <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">To the unlucky person sent to man this one outpost,</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Stating my name now would be somewhat of a waste of time, but if you've gotten this far, you can figure out that I was important. I will not exist, but this file will continue to exist as long as the special machine I used to write it continues to exist. And I don't even know where that thing is, so this file is secured.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">You are on an island off the coast of another bigger island that used to exist near the North Pole of Earth. It's a small island, and only 50 other outposts are out there, manned by 49 other people. There has only been one continent on Earth since its beginning: Asia, with China, East Africa, and Oceania being the main parts of the continent. We have some proof of prior continents existing, before The Child got to them. </span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Your job is simple. Kill The Child. The Child's name is Smith, and he does not exist. How you will accomplish this is up to you, but take your time. You have all the time in the world.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">The Child came from a country that did not know of the rest of the World. They only knew the several other islands that surrounded it. In 2001, it ceased to exist. The two huge continents to the very West have always existed to him, and will continue to exist to him. He lives in a normal world. They just don't exist to us. Not anymore.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">You have roughly 50 years to complete your task. This is what I mean all the time in the world. At 30 years, the moon will disappear, and at 50 years, The Sun. This will kill The Child, but I'd rather it not get to that point. Get going.</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Oh, and you also have a secondary objective...</span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty></span>
  <span data-ty data-ty-prompt="|">Remember us.</span>


</div>

<!-- include and initialise termynal.js -->
<script src="https://cdn.rawgit.com/deadsurgeon42/scp-sources/6cf60652/scp-4000-samualism/termynal.js" data-termynal-container="#termynal"></script>

</body>
[[/html]]
@@ @@
@@ @@
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
